>mono-repos</li>\n<li>design patterns (e.g., model-view-controller)</li>\n<li>semantic versioning</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/gxt00gigj1vgfc9gayv9q1o\">1. Core Capabilities</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/bdlqteih3cytl4ahfyl48og\">Developer Decompose Project</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/gcx7j3slce2kb38rqjy05xs\">Developer Organize Projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/gsrjh2z5wb4nysbflzwn0ts\">Developer Reuse Elements of External Projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/75ssft5a3d4zge2al7kydic\">Developer Reuse Elements of This Project</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"grm72euar5jvm3g7039hzc9","title":"OSHW Project Management User Stories","desc":"","updated":1730492720315,"created":1727814145470,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"user-stories"},"contentHash":"a58f008dac7f69513dec9e1de9444f92","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"grm72euar5jvm3g7039hzc9","vaultName":"user-stories"},"value":"0-workshop","alias":"0-workshop","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":4,"offset":326},"end":{"line":6,"column":18,"offset":340},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"0-workshop"}},{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"root","id":"grm72euar5jvm3g7039hzc9","vaultName":"user-stories"},"value":"0-workshop","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":372},"end":{"line":10,"column":16,"offset":387},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"0-workshop"}}],"anchors":{"preamble":{"type":"header","text":"Preamble","value":"preamble","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"0-workshop":{"type":"header","text":"0-workshop","value":"0-workshop","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["xox7exjnhcxnab73bxyrblt","py9pnyni5n8iwwbgqmfsad1","x9z2rffos85uyh5a7c1xmh2","8655o7b563qlvdmr8bh7reg","u4pvwq8xtlj4awlt51jjzow"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n## Preamble\n\nWelcome to the *How do you share your Open-Source Hardware proj